import { createApp } from 'vue'
import Vue from 'vue'
import App from './App.vue'


import newThing from './newComponent.vue'



import router from './router/index.js'


import store from './store'

Vue.config.productionTip = false

new Vue({
    router,
    store,
    render: h => h(App),
}).$mount('#app')


createApp(App).mount('#app')


new Vue({
    render:h=> h(newThing),
}).$mount('#newSpace')
